(97, 1, 'Ring Ceremony', '&lt;h3&gt;&lt;marquee behavior=&quot;scroll&quot; direction=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;This is to inform to all our valuable customers that Booking for Flowers, Puja Kits, Prasad Kit, Monthly Puja Kit will start from 27th June 2016&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/marquee&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;According to Hindu traditions, the&amp;nbsp;engagement ceremony is done a few months before the marriage. This ceremony is a&amp;nbsp;formal announcement of the impending marriage and the start of the planning for&amp;nbsp;the big event.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Ring Ceremony', '', '', '', ''),
