mal&quot;;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-priority:99;\r\n	mso-style-qformat:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:&quot;&quot;;\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin-top:0in;\r\n	mso-para-margin-right:0in;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:10.0pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin-left:0in;\r\n	line-height:115%;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:11.0pt;\r\n	font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\n	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n	mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;![endif]--&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Privacy&lt;/strong&gt;: Prabhujionline will never share any of your\r\npersonal information with any third party.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Satisfaction Guaranteed&lt;/strong&gt;: At Prabhujionline we believe in 100%\r\ncustomer satisfaction and we will work to achieve this goal.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Payment&lt;/strong&gt;: Prabhujionline accepts American Express, Visa,\r\nMasterCard and Discover credit cards, as well as Paypal. We also accept\r\npersonal checks, money orders, and bank wires. Payments must first clear before\r\nproducts are shipped.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Returns&lt;/strong&gt;: Prabhujionline will accept returns on any\r\npurchases within 30 days for money back, exchange, or credit. No questions\r\nasked! Shipping charges are refunded on returns that are the fault of Lotus\r\nSculpture, or if there is the unlikely event of damage during shipping. Prabhujionline\r\ndoes not refund shipping charges if the customer simply does not like the item.\r\nA 3% service charge is applied to returns. The return fee and shipping charges\r\nare waived if Prabhujionline or the shipping company is at fault. If the\r\ncustomer is returning the product, it must be sent back fully insured and postage\r\npaid to Lotus Sculpture. Please contact us before returning the product.&amp;nbsp;\r\nOnly after the return is received and the statue is in good condition will the\r\nrefund be issued.&amp;nbsp; For all statues being returned by freight the customer\r\nis responsible for the crating of the sculpture.&amp;nbsp; The same rules apply to\r\ncrated returns; if the customer simply does not like the statue then the\r\ncustomer must pay the shipping to and the return fees.&amp;nbsp; If there is\r\nsomething wrong with the sculpture then Prabhujionline pays the return shipping\r\nfee.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'privacy and return', '', ''),
